{"tid":2447413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始：疫苗接種情況不理想  或收緊社交措施  難放寬跨境旅行","createTime":"2021-03-15T07:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T08:18:53.000Z","uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c29bd3ede4b3df8c077bd0ae839cd66420a1970","tid":2447413,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"非黃營link: [url]<a href=\"https://topick.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hk&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=36b6374f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hk</a><del><a href=\"http://et.com/article/2901491/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%9A%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%8E%87%E6%8F%90%E5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fet.com%2Farticle%2F2901491%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%2582%2587%25E5%25A7%258B%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%258E%2587%25E6%258F%2590%25E5&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=04599d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">et.com/article/2901491/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E8%82%87%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%9A%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%8E%87%E6%8F%90%E5</a></del>%8D%87%E3%80%80%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%94%BE%<ins>E5%AF%AC%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%86%E9%99%90%E5%88</ins>%B6%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BE%A9%E8%AA%B2[/url]<br />\n<br />\n她指，上周五（12日）目前疫情接種情況附合預期，與其他地方接種的經驗相約。對於有個別人士曾接種疫苗後死亡或出現異常反應，她強調專家委員會評估的結果顯示疫苗與死亡未有因果關係，稍後專家委員會將會研究最新個案。<br />\n陳肇始表示，放寬社交距離有機會反彈，確診數字維持雙位數高位，加上疫苗接種情況未如理想，不排除有機會收緊社交措施。<br />\n她指，若疫苗接種理想，加上做好嚴守防疫措施，其他商業措施或有機會放寬，學校可恢復正常等。她更強調，疫苗接種率亦是未來恢復跨境出行及作為放寬跨境旅行的重要考慮。"},{"pid":"fa1459030465588ee52d2faf33f7a81b2ff123c1","tid":2447413,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:36:55.0